</p>
<p>Make it extend a class called <code>JsonHalSerializer</code>: this is the current class responsible
for adding links in the HAL format. In fact: open up the class.</p>
<p>It has two method. <code>serializeLinks()</code> is responsible for reading the <code>Relation</code> annotations
and adding them to the JSON with <code>_links</code>. <code>serializeEmbeddeds()</code> adds any embedded
relations under the <code>_embedded</code> key.</p>
<p>For now, let's focus on changing how the links render only. Go to the "Code"-&gt;"Generate"
menu - <code>command</code>+<code>N</code> on a Mac - and hit "Override Methods". Override <code>serializeLinks()</code>:</p>
